Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,友軍?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.70,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad0\fs35\frz18.27\pos(777,434)}孤身二人的謀反者們
