Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.34,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad0\fs35\frz18.27\pos(699.667,422)}這下今天是完美的一天了!
